About us
Mugs N' Jugs Family Grille is a great place for lunch, dinner, and family fun. We offer a wide selection of food and have Daily specials. There are 2 game rooms for the kids and pool tables for all ages. We offer a full liquor bar as well as an outside bar and patio seating for smoking and enjoying the Florida weather.
There is Karaoke every Friday and Saturday, as well as a Jukebox in the poolroom and outside bar. We offer Cornhole Tournaments Wednesdays and Fridays, as well as Charity Quarter Auctions every 3rd Wednesday with Bailey's Way Dog Rescue.
